00:05:25.630 --> 00:05:28.850
divided by g, and then
this is going to be meters.

00:05:28.850 --> 00:05:31.210
And so what is this going to roughly be?

00:05:31.210 --> 00:05:33.360
Well h is going to be approximately,

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:36.330
let's say that g is approximately
10 meters per second,

00:05:36.330 --> 00:05:39.500
